 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amstel Gold Race\", \"from\": 8362, \"to\": 8378}, {\"ngram\": \"a palmar\\u00e8s\", \"from\": 8382, \"to\": 8392}, {\"ngram\": \"conjunction\", \"from\": 8422, \"to\": 8433}, {\"ngram\": \"other disciplines\", \"from\": 8439, \"to\": 8456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, Pidcock is also the reigning Olympic champion in mountain bike and will be out to defend that title five days before the road race.\", \"from\": 8458, \"to\": 8598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 8461, \"to\": 8465}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 8467, \"to\": 8474}, {\"ngram\": \"the reigning Olympic champion\", \"from\": 8483, \"to\": 8512}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain bike\", \"from\": 8516, \"to\": 8529}, {\"ngram\": \"that title\", \"from\": 8556, \"to\": 8566}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 8584, \"to\": 8597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fred Wright is a proven Tour of Flanders top-10 rider, Stevie Williams won Fl\\u00e8che Wallonne this spring, and Tarling can never be underestimated as he doubles up with the TT, but it's Pidcock who's realistically GB's leading light here.\", \"from\": 8599, \"to\": 8834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8599, \"end\": 8610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Wright_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9999956969842781, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Wright_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Wright_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 8654, \"end\": 8669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stevie Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Williams\"}, {\"begi