an\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzie_Deignan\"}, {\"begin\": 8982, \"end\": 8989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999999843521438, \"rank\": 1.5647843991284265e-08, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 9033, \"end\": 9041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.03501069390613e-53, \"text\": \"Classics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's side\", \"from\": 8946, \"to\": 8962}, {\"ngram\": \"a former world champion\", \"from\": 9002, \"to\": 9025}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic silver medallist\", \"from\": 9056, \"to\": 9080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's now 35 and has not won a race since she landed the inaugural Paris-Roubaix Femmes in 2021, although she has always stepped up to the plate in international events, as recently as last year's Worlds, where she was sixth.\", \"from\": 9092, \"to\": 9317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9159, \"end\": 9172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9824390445527784, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 9121, \"to\": 9127}, {\"ngram\": \"the plate\", \"from\": 9227, \"to\": 9236}, {\"ngram\": \"international events\", \"from\": 9240, \"to\": 9260}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's Worlds\", \"from\": 9277, \"to\": 9295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deignan might well injure something but if represents more of the past, then the future appears to belong to Pfeiffer Georgi.\", \"from\": 9319, \"to\": 9444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9319, \"end\": 9326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herbert_Girton_Deignan\", \"score\": 0.9999999696428863, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Deignan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herbert_Girton_Deignan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Herbert_Girton_Deignan\"}, {\"begin\": 9428, \"end\": 9443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfeiffer_Georgi\", \"score\": 0.9999994495557681, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pfeiffer Georgi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfeiffer_Georgi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pfeiffer_Georgi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 9345, \"to\": 9354}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 9381, \"to\": 9389}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 9396, \"to\": 9406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old has really started to hit her stride now and still has bags of potential to explore.\", \"from\": 9445, \"to\": 9545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her stride\", \"from\": 9487, \"to\": 9497}, {\"ngram\": \"bags\", \"from\": 9516, \"to\": 9520}, {\"ngram\": \"potential\", \"from\": 9524, \"to\": 9533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She retained her British national champion's jersey last month, in a season in which she made a Classics breakthrough with a podium at Paris-Roubaix.\", \"from\": 9546, \"to\": 9695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9563, \"end\": 9588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British national champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 9642, \"end\": 9650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Classic_cycle_races\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.03501069390613e