a.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.99820326981176, \"rank\": 0.0017999642383815055, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the European Championships\", \"from\": 9991, \"to\": 10017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the sheer depth of competition, a medal will be a tall order but she will want to be knocking on the door.\", \"from\": 10019, \"to\": 10131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sheer depth\", \"from\": 10025, \"to\": 10040}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 10044, \"to\": 10055}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 10057, \"to\": 10064}, {\"ngram\": \"a tall order\", \"from\": 10073, \"to\": 10085}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 10122, \"to\": 10130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mountain biking was only added to the Olympic programme in 1996, with just the Cross-Country discipline included.\", \"from\": 10135, \"to\": 10248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mountain biking\", \"from\": 10135, \"to\": 10150}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic programme\", \"from\": 10169, \"to\": 10190}, {\"ngram\": \"just the Cross-Country discipline\", \"from\": 10205, \"to\": 10238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain had never won a medal until Tom Pidcock turned up in Tokyo and stormed off with gold, one of a number of breakthrough moments in his nascent career.\", \"from\": 10249, \"to\": 10405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10249, \"end\": 10256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999999843521438, \"rank\": 1.5647843991284265e-08, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 10285, \"end\": 10296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Pidcock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\"}, {\"begin\": 10310, \"end\": 10315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999064320894714, \"rank\": 9.357666605295794e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 10271, \"to\": 10278}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 10337, \"to\": 10341}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 10350, \"to\": 10358}, {\"ngram\": \"breakthrough moments\", \"from\": 10362, \"to\": 10382}, {\"ngram\": \"his nascent career\", \"from\": 10386, \"to\": 10404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock will be out to defend his title and will be the favourite for the gold medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 10407, \"to\": 10501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10495, \"end\": 10500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.218279117632644e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 10407, \"to\": 10414}, {\"ngram\": \"his title\", \"from\": 10437, \"to\": 10446}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 10477, \"to\": 10491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old's efforts on the road and in cyclo-cross have not dampened his mountain biking talents - in fact, he has said he was 'born to mountain bike - and he has dipped in this season to take some commanding wins, notably at Nove Mesto and Crans Montana.\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10755, \"end\": 10762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montana\", \"score\": 0.9999962596036234, \"rank\": 3.723743517075443e-06, \"text\": \"Montana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://d